{
  "logNo": "222910453373",
  "title": "[기획] 스토리보딩 작업 Part Ⅰ,  온보딩(Onboarding)",
  "addDate": "2022. 10. 25.",
  "categoryNo": "22",
  "url": "https://m.blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/222910453373",
  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-19372ec4-c0a6-4d13-968b-c0ef27c3af8f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2b83a215-27eb-4c3f-b5cf-539ccb5b87d4\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1cd7e190-fc39-4d18-bf5a-5a620b0e34be\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Story Boarding DAY 28</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3309de1f-5c08-4f2c-a3fd-b6eb75d2d151\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d698d078-23f0-4080-9235-dac20297ea9f\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-803f4a89-0392-4fdf-8d13-2c0dc0fb6d97\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a8e056c7-4997-4aed-aa06-985338349aa2\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>[본격적인 스토리보딩 작업]</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-13914e6c-f2d2-4364-b992-cad90cd57421\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-719080d4-c68d-401a-827d-faff6d6346c2\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>이제 본격적으로 스토리보딩 작업에 들어갑니다. 지금까지는 자료나 개념에 대해 심도있게 생각했습니다. 물론 아직은 미흡한 부분이나 보강해야하는 사항이 있지만 앞으로 채워나가도록 하겠습니다. 이제부터는 하나하나 PPT 파일을 정리하도록 하겠습니다. 이제 시작입니다. 약 두달 뒤 나름 완벽한 (주)파파스컴퍼니 기획문서가 완성되기를 희망해 봅니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-default\" id=\"SE-87dafdef-fda6-4225-a9e5-47ae74c2cd5d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-default\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-47f3dab1-34b6-47af-9d66-2f8d3d3ca6c9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2ff7b80d-c5bb-4580-8dc2-29b0c47be254\" style=\"color:#424242;\"><b>자유로운 사람만이 느낄 수 있는 기쁨이라고 생각한다. 희망의 긴 여행을 떠나는 자유로운 사람. 태평양이 내 꿈에서처럼 푸르기를 희망한다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-cite\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-79b6f8d7-68ff-4171-8157-e81bff91eaa4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-1b9b95c6-e5ff-4a0a-867f-bf26c9a41aed\" style=\"\">쇼생크탈출</span></p></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-54ac836a-38a3-41a4-bc16-159405735de1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:709px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-54ac836a-38a3-41a4-bc16-159405735de1\", \"src\" : \"https://blogfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMTdfOCAg/MDAxNjY2MDE2ODQxNzAw.MFPetfRtOqhnhNPL2ZtpwJQPxy3mIHCObsRBsGxFTwgg.9d_41_rHel6pNsefPz-V3mzb09OvOCzPZSDPVlEc-iEg.PNG.cookthedesign/Untitled-1.png?type=w1\", \"originalWidth\" : \"709\", \"originalHeight\" : \"60\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://blogfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMTdfOCAg/MDAxNjY2MDE2ODQxNzAw.MFPetfRtOqhnhNPL2ZtpwJQPxy3mIHCObsRBsGxFTwgg.9d_41_rHel6pNsefPz-V3mzb09OvOCzPZSDPVlEc-iEg.PNG.cookthedesign/Untitled-1.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-14d5c668-3e5a-4209-8c2c-ba84ccb28e85\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e3dd68d4-a59d-42ef-8f82-862550ba5265\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-68286ab0-c6cc-4ad8-9ea9-e2c30d4a2f33\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Tip1. 위치, 배치에 따른 UI</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b2f69500-a4b2-43ac-89cc-5a53788ed90d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-04a530bb-f3a2-4e7d-bd04-6bc2b1a5ddad\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Tip2. 클릭, 이벤트와 연동</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6dacec58-883c-486f-a0d1-14b69769de12\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-707a18c2-ffba-490d-852f-265b28e9a7f0\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Tip3. 중복과 모양</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-21e75ce9-b072-4e9a-bf17-f35da4068b55\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f2802cd3-420e-4cfa-b963-132d734653aa\" style=\"color:#ff0010;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Tip4. 프로세스에 맞는 구성</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d8e8135d-b49a-448c-94db-5d065a70b3dc\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2506e54a-0231-4f34-8d7a-0c492f1dea08\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Tip5. 정확한 전달</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-36caf0a6-984b-4f50-9ffc-6be204bff414\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-88539ecc-51c5-4453-9b7e-32eaa7973048\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a3a080a7-2efa-4c6b-995f-3a1a2de14512\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a3c7870b-e818-4814-9ed7-5b47c008c1ac\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">모바일 UI 구성시 주의사항을 계속해서 올립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e08ad06e-f00c-478f-b508-5e6d28c25bb6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-fdd86112-33f7-4ed1-b6c6-b320e326f1e8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d51a13d2-e0d3-4810-8349-53613ac3fc56\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6cfec30d-272f-44e6-8763-d779498b99c7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1f79356d-e2b2-4de4-a0de-466deed2f884\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a9d57eb4-4cd8-4b1e-8911-c3af3cb600cc\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Tip4. 프로세스에 맞는 구성</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9b1e280a-109b-420a-b96c-b0048a16e41f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-9b1e280a-109b-420a-b96c-b0048a16e41f\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMjVfMjM3/MDAxNjY2NjkzNDUzODk1.ldfvEfqz36n4Zf9JlUxbiBZClmceLMqT_MeMdMu3D6Ug.Ck75Wj_iYBomQoOLWChAilN-9xfY3oT9U5qHtn3ghukg.PNG.cookthedesign/91%EC%8A%A4%ED%86%A0%EB%A6%AC%EB%B3%B4%EB%93%9C_%EC%9E%91%EC%97%85_221024.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2718\", \"originalHeight\" : \"2718\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMjVfMjM3/MDAxNjY2NjkzNDUzODk1.ldfvEfqz36n4Zf9JlUxbiBZClmceLMqT_MeMdMu3D6Ug.Ck75Wj_iYBomQoOLWChAilN-9xfY3oT9U5qHtn3ghukg.PNG.cookthedesign/91%EC%8A%A4%ED%86%A0%EB%A6%AC%EB%B3%B4%EB%93%9C_%EC%9E%91%EC%97%85_221024.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-820a7685-d96c-427d-8db1-567184308248\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-074794c5-3187-4be9-9a6f-99b8630e30b6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4cc78035-d208-4939-9e87-bf9f8eae82ab\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-08a598f6-7854-4a22-b338-d873f9083b87\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-08a598f6-7854-4a22-b338-d873f9083b87\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMjVfMjM1/MDAxNjY2NjkzNDg3MzA1.nGz4-21HtZBRsNUEnB1aqXWs8NWrDQQIvJefyYeqVx0g.EL0PGP62P_YpJFV8xZ4Jp4NjkWqDQYVTBt6kwU6R5vcg.PNG.cookthedesign/91%EC%8A%A4%ED%86%A0%EB%A6%AC%EB%B3%B4%EB%93%9C_%EC%9E%91%EC%97%85_221024.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2717\", \"originalHeight\" : \"2304\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMjVfMjM1/MDAxNjY2NjkzNDg3MzA1.nGz4-21HtZBRsNUEnB1aqXWs8NWrDQQIvJefyYeqVx0g.EL0PGP62P_YpJFV8xZ4Jp4NjkWqDQYVTBt6kwU6R5vcg.PNG.cookthedesign/91%EC%8A%A4%ED%86%A0%EB%A6%AC%EB%B3%B4%EB%93%9C_%EC%9E%91%EC%97%85_221024.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-592e2541-779d-41e0-a982-ea331493a58f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d1be1221-0cca-426b-b200-deba06ab02c6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-71e83fe2-7947-4e11-93f8-95b3ef679566\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-41989fa4-ed25-44ef-91e5-98088df64a29\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6efad75a-588c-459d-aef7-96b278075039\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ff2d66a3-7f63-4311-9e20-95e4aad6c16e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a78c04ef-8848-4187-9bf3-fc0eca29ca0f\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>온보딩 스토리보드</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3b3140c0-54a2-4525-a95f-1d90a7e8d9e9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-029f3387-ffae-49a6-b88f-cffe04f5fe73\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">앱에서 온보딩이란 앱 인터페이스를 임팩트있게 사용자에게 제공하는 역할을 합니다. 튜토리얼과는 다른 개념으로 앱 사용설명보다는 실제 앱이 추구하는 방향을 자연스럽게 흐름도처럼 구축하는게 중요합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4226c171-3c6e-4b27-adb8-51c360ab9cef\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8f0311ad-a3c1-40c1-a900-8e126e837a33\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0ba3010f-85e7-4f23-a02e-286dcc26893a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-15d1d707-5cb9-4dc4-a378-cc83a838c82f\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>튜토리얼</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs11 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b464da0f-075f-411d-9e3a-79dc753658a9\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"> </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a794e576-391e-4ea0-80d1-74fb079f5ddc\" style=\"color:#666666;background-color:#ffffff;\">tutorial</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-93d4e647-041a-417a-9a60-838249299c8a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8353a6ea-255d-41e6-81d1-37a1eca496f8\" style=\"color:#7a96b9;background-color:#ffffff;\">명사</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5353c3e9-bf9b-47b0-a241-2c32363f5620\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"> </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d75f1d34-209b-4578-9999-4ba8203971f3\" style=\"color:#888888;background-color:#ffffff;\">예체능 일반</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d85c9872-e69d-487a-8540-42971f4d34f1\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"> 소프트웨어나 하드웨어를 움직이는 데 필요한 사용 지침 따위의 정보를 알려 주는 시스템. 앱에서는 앱 사용설명서라고 보시는게 편합니다. 특히 게임설명 튜토리얼이 이해가 빠르실겁니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-de904b37-a602-4353-b3c0-5bf54c1a209a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-611001fc-cdf4-4ef3-b6dd-2bc6ed29b56a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-77ab1dda-675d-4b5a-9534-149c0b155f53\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-bacdfeec-f85a-4e63-93e2-15944f8a6671\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">요즘 앱에서 추구하는 온보딩은 기능성과 데이터 매칭, 그리고 인터페이스 접목이라는 방향으로 진행됩니다. (주)파파스컴퍼니의 온보딩은 디자인을 서칭하고 그 데이터를 매칭해서 메인페이지로 이동하고 중간에 취지를 알려주는 페이지로 만들어 보겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-33580b57-47bc-480e-b4f9-6635b8404b10\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3cd09b88-6a95-474b-a622-252d3c3c75f1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align- se-l-default\" style=\"max-width:334px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-0a7b0da6-1a24-456f-a392-742618458895\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-51973ca8-48be-4141-9e49-b056d3609734\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d06558c8-2442-45d9-9600-301b7f135148\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4915ab5e-165c-485d-a25b-36984dcc96a1\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">Q보이스 온보딩을 통해 대략적인 이해를 도와드리고자 합니다. 튜토리얼은 아니지만 (주)파파스컴퍼니이 무엇을 하는 앱인지 모르는 상태를 약간의 지침표같은 느낌으로 제작해 보겠습니다. 스플래시와 온보딩은 첫접속자를 위해서만 만들 수 도 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2ae9819a-3044-45d6-b705-8f3d55fa607d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-480d62e7-ca49-48a5-8e3d-77dc18474d3b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-545d7df8-828e-45d7-8010-51efb3b16cee\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e116554b-7782-4e43-9e71-aeadb0c52933\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!--